"NOT FOUND"|"The 44 ablative of degree of difference *** is also instrumental; e.g. paucis ante diebus, a few days before is really before by a few days. Likewise the ***ablatives of price,*** 44 measure,*** and ***fullness *** ; e.g. 441 value a thing by so much (viginti minis) in the scale of price.***The preposition with the instrumental ablative is properly only cum. Other prepositions, such as ab with ablative of agent, have come in by confusion."

