"ubi iam se ad eam rem paratos esse arbitrati sunt, oppida sua omnia, numero ad duodecim, vicos ad quadringentos, reliqua privata aedificia incendunt;   frumentum omne, praeter quod secum portaturi erant, comburunt, ut DOMUM REDITIONIS spe sublata paratiores ad omnia pericula subeunda essent; trium mensum molita cibaria sibi quemque domo efferre iubent."|"domum reditionis, hope of a return home. domum is the accusative of limit of motion after the verbal noun reditionis. These nouns in tio in early Latin governed a direct object through the influence of a verbal notion ; manus (probably accusative) iniectio esto, let there be a laying on of hands. (Laws of Twelve Tables, III.) The ***gerund*** and ***supine*** are simple verbal nouns. There is no difference between reditionis spe and redeundi spe."

