"qua de causa helvetii quoque reliquos gallos virtute praecedunt, quod fere cotidianis proeliis cum germanis contendunt, cum aut suis finibus eos prohibent aut ipsi IN EOrum finibus bellum gerunt."|"5. in eo flumine. Note that English over cannot be rendered by trans in such an expression. The bridge is on (over) the stream, trans would imply it was on the other side, e.g. qui trans Rhenum incolunt."

